### Variables
@token = your-jwt-token-here
@bookingId = 1

### Create a booking (to have something to update)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "barberId": 1,
  "serviceId": 1,
  "bookingDate": "2025-11-20",
  "startTime": "10:00",
  "paymentMethod": "pay_online"
}

### Get a specific booking by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update booking - reschedule to new date and time
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingDate": "2025-11-25",
  "startTime": "14:30"
}

### Update booking
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingDate": "2025-11-22",
  "startTime": "10:00"
}

### Update booking
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingDate": "2025-11-20",
  "startTime": "15:00"
}

### Get customer's bookings
GET http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/customer/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cancel a booking
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all bookings (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all bookings filtered by status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/all?status=PENDING
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all bookings filtered by date
GET http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/all?date=2025-11-20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Mark booking as completed (Barber/Admin only)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Mark booking as paid (Barber/Admin only)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/mark-paid
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Mark booking as no-show (Barber/Admin only)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/no-show
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

